BES Spreadsheetsmith PST Doug Take a look at this spreadsheet I made and let me know what you think It takes the BES interval prices from the operating day reports and computes the following Hourly average for each zone Hourly average ERCOT wide Daily peak average by zone and ERCOT wide Daily offpeak average by zone and ERCOT wide It only is updated as often as they update their operating reports but I think its still a useful tool for looking at prices over time Maybe will benefit from some graphs spreads both Ryan Ryan Williams East Power Trading Enron North America
